<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        .body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #1e40af;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 22px;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Badge verde para éxito */
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            color: #166534;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 13px;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .main-info {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #edf2f7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .main-info th {
            background: #f7fafc;
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #edf2f7;
        }

        .main-info td {
            padding: 15px 10px;
            color: #2d3748;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #edf2f7;
        }

        /* Estilo de caja de confirmación positiva */
        .success-box {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: left;
            margin: 0 5px;
        }

        .success-box strong {
            color: #166534;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .success-text {
            color: #15803d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #a0aec0;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid #edf2f7;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="body">
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Metas Perú S.A.C</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="status-badge">✔ HORA EXTRA APROBADA</div>
            <p style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 25px;">Estimado(a) colaborador(a), su solicitud de
                hora extra ha sido validada y aprobada correctamente.</p>

            <table class="main-info">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Tienda</th>
                        <th>Fecha</th>
                        <th>H. Extra</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="font-weight: bold; color: #1e40af;">{{tienda}}</td>
                        <td>{{fecha}}</td>
                        <td style="font-family: monospace; font-weight: bold;">{{horas}}</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #a0aec0; margin-top: 25px;">Responsable de validación:
                {{usuario_responsable}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            Este es un correo informativo del Sistema de Gestión de Tiempos.<br>
            © 2026 Metas Perú S.A.C
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>